description:
A response to a video titled, "Culling Carnivorous Animals Debate With Vegan Footsoldier", found here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jIBNUwpWbvo  Shout out to @Tess Begg —who, I hope, finally went back to high school, as she's stopped making youtube videos.  Support the creation of new content on the channel (and speak to me, directly, if you want to) via Patreon, for $1 per month: https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel
Why are comments disabled on my youtube channel?  Here's the answer, in a relatively uplifting 5 minute video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EHb9k30KTXM
A searchable list of all of my videos (more effective than searching within youtube, IMO) can be found here: https://aryailia.github.io/a-bas-le-ciel/all.html
Find me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/a_bas_le_ciel/?hl=en
à-bas-le-ciel is not my only youtube channel… there is, in fact, another channel that has my own legal name, Eisel Mazard: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuxp5G-XFGcH4lmgejZddqA/videos
#vegan #vegans #veganism
